(57,	'Luton Airport Parking',	'luton-airport-parking',	'AP',	'26',	'Luton Airport Car Parking - Compare Parking Deals with ParkingZone',	'luton meet and greet parking,luton park and ride,long stay parking luton, short stay parking luton,car parking,parking at airport',	'Book secure and safe Luton airport parking to get hassle-free traveling experience with ParkingZone. Get cheap meet and greet, park and ride and on-site parking services from us.',	'Yes',	'<!-- Airport Paking section --->\r\n<div class=\"tab-pane fade active in\" id=\"parking\">\r\n<h3>Luton Airport Parking</h3><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Luton Airport is the\r\nfifth largest as well as the busiest airport of the UK. It is the only airport\r\nwhich is serving Luton and it’s the neighbourhood. The place is always crowded\r\nwith people and parking at Luton Airport has always been an issue which is now\r\nsolved by the ParkingZone. ParkingZone is the best service which you can use\r\nto book a parking place at any moment of the day. Our website is up for 24/7\r\nand you can scroll our comparison list for parking lots at any time. </span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">ParkingZone services\r\nare cheaper, reliable, trusted and time-saving. We have strict security\r\npolicies and we are working with those parking providers who can fulfill our\r\nsecurity policies. Your car will be under observation for 24 hours and the\r\nlatest CCTV cameras will make sure that vehicles are safe while you are away\r\nfrom your city. You can find the parking services of Meet & Greet in which\r\nyour car will be parked by the driver or you can use the Park & Ride\r\nservice in which you can park your car yourself. You can also use On-Airport\r\nparking service in which you can park your vehicle at the airport and walk by\r\nthe terminal within a minute.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n</span><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"> </span></p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n</span></div><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n</span><!-- train section ---><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n</span><div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"overview\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n</span><h3>Luton Airport Overview</h3><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">The Airport started\r\nits services in 1938 when it was designed for military purposes.  </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">When World War II was over, the airport was\r\nopened for the commercial flights as well. London Luton Airport is known as one\r\nof the best airports for commercial flights. The Airport is providing its best\r\nfacilities to almost 15 Million passengers yearly. The airport has only one\r\nrunway as well as a single terminal. The airport is also opened for the private\r\njets, leisure flights, and business tours. Most of its destinations include the\r\nUK and Europe.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:200%\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Direction</span><o:p></o:p></b></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">If you are travelling\r\ntowards the airport from a Rural area then you should use the Google navigation\r\nmap to locate the closest highway which will further lead you to the airport.\r\nLuton is located 30 miles away from the northwest of London and 32 Miles away\r\nfrom Central London. You should use your own vehicle to reach the airport since\r\nthe airport is far off from the main city. Using your own vehicle can become a\r\nheadache for you if you will not find a parking lot at the terminal. Therefore,\r\nyou can book a parking place by going to the ParkingZone website. We are\r\nworking with parking operators and providing you with the cheapest rates. You\r\ncan also avail discounts by getting our services.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n</span></div><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n</span><!-- hotel search ---><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n</span><div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"fac\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n</span><h3>Airport Facilities</h3><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">London Luton Airport\r\nis providing the best facilities to its customers. The airport has only a\r\nsingle terminal and you can find everything under a single roof. You can enjoy\r\nshopping, have food and many more exciting things. Following is a list of\r\nfacilities provided by the London Luton Airport.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 200%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 200%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">●</span><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">     \r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\