<b><br></b></p><div class=\"col-sm-6\"><ul class=\"facilites-points-stmp\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>\r\n</b></span></ul><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>\r\n</b></span></div><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>\r\n</b></span></div><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>\r\n</b></span><div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"top_things\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>\r\n</b></span><h3>Top things to do in Luton Airport</h3><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:200%\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Comfort</span><o:p></o:p></b></p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">If your flight is\r\ndelayed or you have early at the airport, you can use the VIP lounges where\r\nthere are comfortable armchairs. You can also enjoy free WiFi, charging points\r\nand many more things.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:200%\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Food Items</span><o:p></o:p></b></p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Sometimes, it is a\r\nbig problem to find something delicious to eat at airports. The London Luton\r\nAirport has solved this problem by offering some delicious food items. You can\r\nenjoy continental food items as well as Chinese, Italian and Asian food from\r\nthe resultant.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:200%\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Cafes</span><o:p></o:p></b></p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">If you are not in a\r\nmood to eat something heavier, you can go for something light. You can get\r\ncoffees, sandwiches and fast foods as well.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:200%\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Shopping</span><o:p></o:p></b></p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">If you have some\r\nspare time at the terminal, you can spend it at the shopping center. You can\r\nbuy mobile phone chargers, earphones and gifts for your loved ones.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:200%\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Entertainment</span><o:p></o:p></b></p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">If your flight is\r\ndelayed for 2 to 3 hours then you can hire a car as well as chauffeur and visit\r\nthe whole Luton city. There are many exciting things to explore in Luton city.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n</span></div><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n</span><div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"map\"><center><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n</span><h3><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Map</span></h3><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n</span><br><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n</span><div style=\"width: 100%;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.mapsdirections.info/en/custom-google-maps/map.php?width=100%&height=600&hl=ru&q=luton%20Airport+()&ie=UTF8&t=&z=11&iwloc=B&output=embed\" width=\"100%\" height=\"600\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></div>\r\n</center></div>',	216,	'2018-01-23 07:49:13',	'2018-01-23 07:49:13',	'No',	'Luton Airport Meet & Greet is an easy way to park your car at the parking terminal. All you have to do is to book the meet & greet car parking package from our website and your car will be picked from the terminal once you arrive.',	'If you are looking for cheap Luton airport parking which is also secured and convenient, you can use the park and ride service. Park your car at the booked location and catch your flight through shuttle bus service.',	'We are working with only those parking operators who are fulfilling our strict security protocol. We will provide you with all the options of cheap Luton Airport car parking services. You can get three types of parking services on our website. Following is the list of the services you can get:',	'ParkingZone provides a comparison list of meet & greet parking services at Luton Airport. In meet & greet car parking service, you will meet a person close to the airport terminal and he will park your car. Apart from car parking service, you can also avail the car wash service from the parking operators who are offering car wash services.',	'With Liverpool Park & Ride service you can park your car yourself at a booked location and keep your keys with you. Your car will be parked under the 24/7 surveillance system and you can pick your car once you arrive from your journey. You can also access the terminal within 10 to 15 minutes by using shuttle bus service.',	'Our customers are not restricted to use only these two service. They can also use ParkingZone On-Airport parking option. On Airport car parking is probably the quickest option to park your car at any airport. You can park your car at the terminal and walk to the terminal within a minute or two. <br><br>'),
