p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%\"><o:p> </o:p></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"map\"><center>\r\n<h3>Map</h3>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.mapsdirections.info/en/custom-google-maps/map.php?width=100%&height=600&hl=ru&q=Birmingham%20Airport+()&ie=UTF8&t=&z=12&iwloc=B&output=embed\" width=\"100%\" height=\"600\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></div>\r\n</center></div>',	216,	'2018-01-23 07:42:25',	'2018-01-23 07:42:25',	'No',	'Birmingham meet and greet car parking is the easiest way to park your car at the airport parking lot. You will be guided by a chauffeur and he will meet you at the terminal. The chauffeur will park your car at your booked location and you can get your car back upon your arrival at the terminal on a single phone call.',	'If you don’t want to share your car keys with the chauffeur then you can also park your car yourself at the parking lot.  Park your car and keep your car keys with you. Your car will be watched under the surveillance system for 24/7.',	'ParkingZone has some strict security policies and only those parking fields are listed on the comparison list which fulfil our security policies. You can find three types of parking services at reasonable prices on our website. The parking rates start from  £4 per day and vary on weekly basis. We promise to provide you with the best and cheapest rates. Following are the list of the services you can find at PakingZone.',	'If you don’t want to waste your time at the Airport terminal then you can use the Birmingham meet and greet car parking service. All you have to do is to reach the terminal and call the chauffeur. The chauffeur will meet you at the terminal and park your car at your booked parking lot. We will organize everything for you and you can get your keys back