rt Park and Ride service. After reaching the terminal, you can park your car yourself in the parking lot. You can keep your car keys with you and drive your car upon your arrival from your journey.<br><br><br>',	'We also have a contract with those companies whose parking lots are walking distance away from the terminal. You can park your vehicle there if you’re in a hurry and reach the terminal within minutes.<br><br><br><br><br>'),
(62,	'Manchester Airport Parking',	'manchester-airport-parking',	'AP',	'27',	'Manchester Airport Car Parking - Compare Parking Deals with ParkingZone',	'Manchester meet and greet parking,Manchester  park and ride,Manchester long stay parking, Manchester  short stay parking,car parking,parking at airport',	'Search and save upto 60% while booking manchester airport parking with ParkingZone.Get best deals on the meet and greet, park and ride and on-site parking services.',	'Yes',	'<!-- Airport Paking section --->\r\n<div class=\"tab-pane fade active in\" id=\"parking\">\r\n<h3>Manchester Airport Parking</h3><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Manchester Airport is serving entire Wales and\r\nNorthwestern England. The number of passengers travelling to and from\r\nManchester Airport is increasing each year. The Airport is a few miles away\r\nfrom the town, therefore, public transport or a taxi can cost you much\r\nregarding time as well as money. Bringing your car to reach the terminal won’t\r\nbe a bad idea. Using your own vehicle can decrease your time to reach the\r\nterminal as well as save your cost. It is necessary to book a parking lot for\r\nyour car if you are planning to reach the terminal. ParkingZone helps you to\r\nfind your parking space within a reasonable price. All you have to do is to\r\nselect an airport, enter the drop off date and time, enter the pickup date and\r\ntime, promo code if you have any and click on the search button. There will a\r\nlist of all the available parking space near the airport you have selected. You\r\ncan choose any of the packages you find it suitable. </span><br></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n</span></p></div><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n</span><!-- train section ---><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n</span><div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"overview\">\r\n<h3>Airport Overview</h3><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Manchester\r\nAirport is the third busiest airport in the UK and busiest outside London. The\r\nAirport is serving more than 199 destinations. In 2018, Manchester Airport made\r\na record by handling more than 40 Million passengers. The airport has two\r\nrunways and three terminals named as Terminal 1, Terminal 2, Terminal 3.  </span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">In\r\nthe start, the airport only had a single runway and it was known as the Ridgway\r\nAirport. The construction of the airport was started in early 1937 and it\r\nstarted its operation in 1938.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">  </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">The\r\nAirport is serving almost all of the world and its destinations include African,\r\nAmerican, European as well as Asian cities.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"> \r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">The Airport is serving more than 40 Million passengers yearly and the\r\nnumber is increasing every year.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">The\r\nAirport is located 8 miles away from the Center of the city and it can be\r\naccessed from M56. The Airport has 3 terminals and each terminal has many road\r\nentrances. If you are driving to the terminal for the first time, it is\r\nnecessary to know that which road will connect you to the nearest terminal. You\r\ncan use Google map if you want to avoid any delay. Once you arrive at the\r\nterminal, you will be seeing a lot of traffic and passengers making it\r\ndifficult for you to park your car if y