an></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Kids play\r\narea<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"top_things\"><h3>Top Things To Do</h3><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:8.0pt;line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%\">You can do the following things at\r\nBristol Airport:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:8.0pt;line-height:200%\"><b><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:200%\">VIP treatment<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:8.0pt;line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%\">If you are already tired and want to\r\nskip the crowded areas at the airport, you can buy a VIP voucher with your\r\nticket. You can sit in the VIP lounges and get quick access to the necessary\r\nservices. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:8.0pt;line-height:200%\"><b><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:200%\">Fine Dining<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:8.0pt;line-height:200%\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Bristol International Airport is\r\nalways filled with the crowd. If your flight is delayed or you have arrived\r\nearly at the airport, you can try the food court of the Airport. You can have a\r\nvariety of food items varying from continental food to traditional food items.\r\nThere are also some Asian food items which you can try.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:8.0pt;line-height:200%\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><br></span><b><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:200%\">Multi-Faith prayer room<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:8.0pt;line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%\">People from all over the world travel\r\nevery year from Bristol Airport, therefore, there is a multi-faith prayer room\r\nin which people related to all religion can offer their prayers.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:8.0pt;line-height:200%\"><b><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:200%\">Shopping<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:8.0pt;line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%\">There are different shops at the\r\nairport which are selling some interesting things. You can get gifts as well as\r\nhousehold items from there.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:8.0pt;line-height:200%\"><b><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:200%\">Play area<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:8.0pt;line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%\">There is a play area at the Airport\r\nwhich is specified for the children. The play area is safe and secure and there\r\nare guards who will protect your children from every hurdle.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:8.0pt;line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%\"><o:p> </o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:8.0pt;line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%\"><o:p> </o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:200%\"><o:p> </o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:200%\"><o:p> </o:p></span></p></div>\r\n <div id=\"map\" class=\"tab-pane fade\"></div>',	216,	'2018-01-23 07:52:26',	'2018-01-23 07:52:26',	'No',	'Bristol Airport meet and greet car parking is the hassle-free way to park your car at the airport parking lot. You will be met a chauffeur and he will park your car at your booked location. You can get your car back upon your arrival at the terminal on a single phone call.',	NULL,	'ParkingZone does not compromise the security policies of your car and only those parking fields are listed on the comparison list which fulfils our security policies.  The parking rates are starting from  £4 per day and you can avail discounts as well. We promise to provide you with the best and cheapest parking rates. Following are the list of the services you can find at PakingZone.',	'If you are in a hurry and do not want to waste your time at the Bristol Airport, then you can utilize the meet and greet car parking service. Reach the terminal and call the chauffeur. The chauffeur will meet you at the terminal and park your car at your booked parking lot. The chauffeur is well trained and they will take care of your car.  We will organize everything for you and you can get your keys back once you are done with your trip.',	'If you don’t want to share your keys with the chauffeur then you can use the park and Ride service. After reaching the terminal, call your vehicle at the parking lot and catch a free shuttle bus service to reach the terminal. It will take 10 to15 minutes to reach the terminal.<br><br><br><br><br>',	'You are not restricted to use only above two services. We are also working with those companies who offer parking lots at walking distance away from the terminal. You can park your car on the parking site and reach the terminal within minutes. <br><br><br><br><br><br>'),
(67,	'Leeds Bradford Airport Parking',	'leeds-bradford-airport-parking',	'AP',	'23',	'Leeds Bradford airport Parking | Park And Fly | FlyParkPlus',	'Leeds Bradford  Airport parking,Leeds Bradford car parking,Leeds Bradford park and ride',	'test',	'Yes',	'<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\">Spanning over 2.250KM in overall area, the Leeds Bradford Airport is UK\'s one of premiere airports in both passenger commotion and parking services. With Flypark Plus you can make your stay at this busy airport concise and efficient. Meet &amp; greet, short stay, mid stay, long stay or terminal front express parking; whatever you can think of exists at this airport. With Flypark Plus saving up to 40% is a reality, all you have to do is select a few options and voila, we show you the best deals you can avail to save off both time and money.</span></p>',	1,	'2017-07-27 18:37:06',	'2017-07-27 18:37:06',	'No',	'',	'',	'',	'',	'',	''),
