gZone does not underestimate\r\nthe security policies and we are working with only those parking operators who\r\nare fulfilling our security policies. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:200%\"><b><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:200%\">Directions <o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%\">The airport is at 30 minutes drive\r\nfrom the city centre. You can take one of the following routes to reach the\r\nterminal.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:200%\"><b><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:200%\">Direction From North:<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%\">The airport is located at 17 miles\r\nnorthwest of Belfast City centre. You can take M2 motorway to reach the terminal.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:200%\"><b><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:200%\">Direction From South:<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%\">If you are travelling from South or\r\nWest, you can drive on to the M2 motorway northbound. From M2, turn your car at\r\nMoira junction and travel towards A26. This will lead you to the airport\r\nterminal.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:200%\"><b><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:200%\">Direction For Satellite Navigation:<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN