 passengers can do a\r\nlot of things to enjoy their time. They can go to restaurants with their\r\nfamilies to enjoy traditional food items as well as continental. The airport\r\noffers its facilities for all aged people. Following are the main services of\r\nthe airport:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:200%\"><b><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%\">Food<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:200%\">Food is an essential option at every airport and\r\nAberdeen airport can the best place to find and discover food items. There are\r\nrestaurants who are offering special breakfast meals as well as lunch and\r\ndinner. People can also have coffee and tea if they want to. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:200%\"><b><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%\">Play Area<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:200%\">At Aberdeen International Airport, your children can\r\nhave a good time in the playing area. The play areas are 100% safe for your\r\nchildren and the airport administration has assigned security guards who can\r\ntake care of your children.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:200%\"><b><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%\">Free Makeover<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:200%\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:200%\">You can get a complimentary makeover at the Aberdeen\r\nInternational Airport by asking the staff to give a free makeover.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:200%\"><b><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%\">Business\r\nlounges<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:200