on a single\r\nplatform then there are different restaurants who are offering a lavish buffet\r\nbreakfast. If you have left early from your home or missed the breakfast then\r\nit will be a great option to try Radisson Blu Hotel buffet.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Charging\r\nPhone Facility</span></b><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">If you forgot your charger at home and unfortunately your\r\nphone is not charged then Southampton Airport is offering the services of\r\nmobile phone charging. You can pay a little amount as low as £1 to get your\r\nphone charged.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Keep it\r\nlight </span><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">If you are not in a mood to enjoy buffet breakfast then\r\nyou also have the option to try something light. You can have coffee,\r\nsandwiches and fast food items.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Free\r\nInternet</span><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">If your flight is delayed or you have arrived early at the\r\nairport then you can connect your mobile phone to the high-speed internet and\r\nbrowse social media or watch Youtube videos. The internet services are\r\nabsolutely free and open to everyone.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Meeting\r\nRooms</span><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">There are also some meeting rooms with all the necessary\r\nfacilities. If you are a part of an organization and want to do an emergency\r\nmeeting, you can book the meeting room online or on the spot.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Upgrade to\r\nLuxury:</span><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">If you want to skip the crowd and hustle and bustle of the\r\nairport then you can buy VIP lounge passes along with your ticket. The VIP\r\nlounge is provided with all the necessary facilities like restaurants,\r\ninternet, magazines etc.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><b>\r\n<div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"map\"></div></b>',	216,	'2018-01-23 07:46:14',	'2018-01-23 07:46:14',	'No',	NULL,	NULL,	'With a quick search, you can find the latest parking deals on our website. We will help you to find fascinating deals according to your demand and need. The price to book a slot starts from as low as £4 and you can also get some discounts by using promo code. You can find the following car parking options on our website.',	'With Southampton meet and greet airport parking services, you will be met by a driver who will take care of your car and park your car at your booked location. Let the driver worry about your car parking from the terminal. Give your keys to him and he will park your car on your behalf. You can get your keys back as soon as you will be back from your journey.',	'With Southampton park and Ride services, you can park your car yourself at the parking terminal and get to the terminal quickly. The terminal is usually a few miles away  from such parking area and you can get to the terminal by using a free shuttle bus service provided by the airport.<br><br>',	'These car parking lots are operated by the Airport administration and the terminal is just a walking distance away from the parking. These parking lots are ideal if you want to park your car and access the check-in quickly.<br><br><br><br>'),
(196,	'Airports',	'airports',	'main',	'1',	'Choose Airport Parking for Major Airports Of UK',	'UK airports,airport hotels,airport parking,airport lounges ,travel services deals',	'Find about UK Major airport airport parking ,airport hotels ,affordable airport lounges  information and Flight status before you head to the airport.!',	'Yes',	'<p >With a network of 350+ car parks at more than 30 major airports across the UK, we offer you a chance to capitalize more by spending less regarding comfort, convenience, and value for money. With more than ten years of experience, we are an ideal place to help you out with our meet & greet, park & ride and On-airport parking services. Following are some benefits that you can enjoy with Fly Park Plus.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Say Goodbye to last minute delays - Whether it\'s a weekend trip or long vacation, book your schedule with us and earn a chance to save up to    50% on advanced booking.</li>\r\n<li> From Domestic to International - With our presence across UK\'s major airports, we operate to alleviate your concerns, enabling you to enjoy your trips.</li>\r\n<li> Premium Services in Economical Rates - Our goal is to provide you the best deals for your budget from all the well-known distributors.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 class=\"text-center\">Airport Parking Services</h2>\r\n<p class=\"text-center\">Fly park plus is offering both onsite and offsite parking solutions depending on process set by airport authorities and reputed companies operational structure, normally in airport parking industry there are three types of airport parking services you can book with fly park plus most common types of parking are described below.</p>',	1,	'2017-07-27 10:35:23',	'2017-07-27 10:35:23',	'No',	NULL,	NULL,	NULL,	NULL,	NULL,	NULL),
