(60,	'homepage_tagline_heading',	'We will guide you to find  the best <br/> airport parking space for your car'),
(61,	'homepage_tagline',	'Multiple parking services offer at a single platform'),
(62,	'homepage_howitwork_grid1_heading',	'Search'),
(63,	'homepage_howitwork_grid1_descp',	'You can select the airport you are flying from and the dates you are willing to travel. Click the ‘Search’ button to check the availability of parking space near your airport.'),
(64,	'homepage_howitwork_grid2_heading',	'Select Type'),
(65,	'homepage_howitwork_grid2_descp',	'You can choose any of the car parking offers according to your need. We will provide you with the best travel arrangements.'),
(66,	'homepage_howitwork_grid3_heading',	'Make Payment'),
(67,	'homepage_howitwork_grid3_descp',	'After selecting one of the offers from our comparison list, click on the ‘Make Payment’ button to confirm your booking and to enter your payment details.'),
(68,	'homepage_howitwork_grid4_heading',	'All <br>  Done'),
(69,	'homepage_howitwork_grid4_descp',	'Once you have entered your payment details, we will send a confirmation email and car parking information to your email address.'),
(70,	'homepage_service_heading',	'Services we are offering'),
(71,	'homepage_service_descprition',	'ParkingZone mission is to make your journey easy and hassle-free from any ambiguity. You can get a comparison rate list of airport parking, Airport Lounges as well as Airport Transfer. These lists are updated on daily basis. You can also avail discounts on special occasions.   We are providing the comparison rate list for the following three services.'),
(72,	'homepage_service1',	'Airport Parking'),
(73,	'homepage_service2',	'Airport Lounges'),
(74,	'homepage_service3',	'Airport Transfer'),
(75,	'homepage_whychooseus_grid1_heading',	'Trusted Services'),
(76,	'homepage_whychooseus_grid1_descp',	'The service providers ParkingZone working with are trusted and certified by Park Mark. The Park Mark is a standard of parking providers, which proves that the parking service providers are serious about the safety of the vehicles.'),
(77,	'homepage_whychooseus_grid2_heading',	'Secured Parking'),
(78,	'homepage_whychooseus_grid2_descp',	'The parking service providers we are working with will make your journey hassle-free by taking care of your vehicles. Their 24/7 surveillance system will make your car secure when you are enjoying your journey.'),
(79,	'homepage_whychooseus_grid3_heading',	'Proficient Customer Support'),
(80,	'homepage_whychooseus_grid3_descp',	'Our customer support is available 24/7. You can call at our number at any time of the day. You can Call, email or chat with our expert customer support if you have any query while booking your parking spot.'),
(81,	'homepage_whychooseus_grid4_heading',	'Low Price Guarantee'),
(82,	'homepage_whychooseus_grid4_descp',	'ParkingZone provides you with the lowest prices with our Low Price Guarantee Promise. We compare the prices on a daily basis and make sure that our customers get the cheapest available deals. We back our statements with our low price promise.'),
(83,	'homepage_joinus_heading',	'JOIN US TO RECEIVE'),
(84,	'homepage_joinus_subheading',	'Regular Customer Discount Code'),
(85,	'homepage_joinus_text',	'Sign up today, and we\'ll keep you updated on our discount codes and special offers!'),
(86,	'services_page_parking_heading',	'Airports We Are Servings'),
(87,	'services_page_parking_descp',	'<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ParkingZone is working with trusted parking service providers at multiple airports to provide you with the best comparison rate list. ParkingZone provides you with a chance to spend less money on parking bookings by listing all of the prices near your parking terminal on a comparison list. We are offering the parking comparision lists based on the following airports:       </span></p> <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">1. Aberdeen         2. Bristol           3.Glasgow</span></p> <p>4. Belfast             5. Edinburgh      6. Heathrow</p> <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">7.Birmingham      8. Gatwick          9. Liverpool</span></p> <p>10.Luton              11. Manchester  12. Newcastle                                            </p> <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">13.Southampton  14. Southend     15. Stansted</span></p> <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">                         </span></p> <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You can book the services of meet & greet car parking, Park & Ride and On airport car parking services at the above-mentioned airports with ParkingZone. The parking service providers at these airports are reliable, trusted and equipped with the latest security surveillance systems. </span></p> <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Apart from the parking services, these airports are also equipped with the facilities which are necessary for the passengers. If you have arrived early at the airport or your flight is delayed, you can check in the lavish Airport lounges and VIP hotels, explore the restaurant\'s traditional food and have complimentary drinks in bars.</span></p>'),
(88,	'services_page_parking_sec1_heading',	'AIRPORT PARKING SERVICES'),
(89,	'services_page_parking_sec1_descp',	'ParkingZone is providing onsite as well as offsite parking booking option to its customers depending on the criteria set by the airport administration. In the airport parking industry, there are normally three types of airport parking services and you can book all three with ParkingZone.'),
(90,	'services_page_parking_sec1_meetandgreet',	'One of the easiest and hassle free car parking option. All you have to do is to pre-book this parking package from ParkingZone. You will get a confirmation email as well as you will meet a chauffeur at the airport who will park your car.'),
(91,	'services_page_parking_sec1_parkandride',	'Save your money with ParkingZone and enjoy the cheapest parking rates at the airport. With Park and Ride parking service, you can park your car yourself and reach the terminal by the free shuttle bus service within 10 to 15 minutes.'),
(92,	'services_page_parking_sec1_onairport',	'With On Airport car services, you can park your car at the airport and reach the terminal by walk within 1 to 2 minutes. These parking services are run by the airport administration and you can get your car on your arrival.'),
(93,	'services_page_parking_sec2_heading',	'AIRPORT PARKING IN 3 SIMPLE STEPS'),
(94,	'services_page_parking_sec2_descp',	'ParkingZone airport car offers are just a single click away. You can follow the following simple steps to see the latest car parking price comparison list:'),
(95,	'services_page_parking_sec2_step1',	'Use the search form to fill out the information about your flight. Click on “Get a Quote” once you are done with the information.'),
(96,	'services_page_parking_sec2_step2',	'Choose one of the offers which suit your need. Clicking on the offer will direct you to the payment page.'),
(97,	'services_page_parking_sec2_step3',	'Enter the valid payment details. Once your payment is verified, you will get the booking details on your email id.'),
(98,	'services_page_lounges_heading',	'Airport Lounges We Are Serving'),
(99,	'services_page_lounges_descp',	'If you have arrived early at the airport or in case of flight delay, you don’t have to spend your time in the hustle and bustle of the airport. You can book one of the executive lounges from the price comparison list available on the ParkingZone and enjoy the rest of your time at the lavish executive lounges. These executive lounges are available at cheaper rates and you can a bargain price by in advance. At this price, you will enjoy all of the costly services of lounge-like complimentary crackers, snacks and drinks.  If you are planning to pass your time by eating at the restaurant at the airport or enjoying a coffee, you will probably be spending even more money than spending it on an airport lounge. In the lounges, not only you can enjoy free snacks or drinks but you can also read newspapers, watch your favourite TV shows and enjoy high-speed WiFi internet. These facilities are more appealing than to spend your time at a crowded place. The executive lounge services will make the waiting for the flight more bearable. You usually have to wait for that which is worth waiting for. We understand that your flights are important for you, therefore to minimize your efforts to find a cheap and best business lounge, our website has a comparison list which will help you to find the best business lounge near your airport terminal. The business lounges at the airports will help you to relax until your flight is announced. Book a place in executive lounges via parking zone and avail maximum discounts.'),
(100,	'services_page_lounges_sec1_heading',	'WHEN WOULD I USE AN AIRPORT LOUNGE?'),
(101,	'services_page_lounges_sec1_descp',	'Regardless of whether you are traveling for business or leisure, lounge access can help you make the most of your airport experience.'),
(102,	'services_page_lounges_sec1_grid1',	'One can access the airport lounge regardless of the fact that you are travelling for the purpose of business or for enjoying the holiday. These lounges are available for all aged people.'),
(103,	'services_page_lounges_sec1_grid2',	'One can also book a lounge with an attach kids room. This will provide a safe place for them and you can have some quality family time.'),
(104,	'services_page_lounges_sec1_grid3',	'Enjoy all of the facilities at the lounge in cheaper rates rather than purchasing separate services from the terminal which will cost you more.'),
(105,	'services_page_lounges_sec1_grid4',	'Use the airport lounges to get rid of your tiresome. You can enjoy a shower as well as avail their massage services.'),
(106,	'services_page_lounges_sec2_heading',	'WHAT DO LOUNGES OFFER?'),
(107,	'services_page_lounges_sec2_descp',	'Lounges are often filled with complimentary amenities such as premium food and snacks, fully stocked bars, modern shower facilities, fast WiFi, plentiful power outlets and secure business centers..'),
(108,	'services_page_transfer_heading',	'Airports Transfers'),
(109,	'services_page_transfer_descp',	'Getting from the airport to the hotel can be a headache for you if you are not a local person and not familiar with the local culture. You can be overcharged and the worst case continues if you are not aware of the local language. In such circumstances, passengers are always looking for a reliable and trusted service which can resolve their issues regarding airport transfer. To resolve this problem, ParkingZone also offers the price comparison list of Airport transfer service providers. You can see the package details on the website and book a package according to your needs. These services come in a few different forms. The most famous airport transfer service is the shared airport shuttle which offers a direct transfer service to your lounge or hotel. Passengers can also book the services of a pickup taxi from ParkingZone The taxi will pick the passengers from their home and drop them at the terminal.<br><br><br><br><br><br>'),
(110,	'services_page_transfer_sec1_bestprice',	'ParkingZone provides you best price comparison from the trusted service providers. Book any offer from our website and get the discount now!'),
(111,	'services_page_transfer_sec1_bestsevices',	'We have strict security policies and only those service providers are allowed to collaborate with ParkingZone who can fulfil our criteria.'),
(112,	'services_page_transfer_sec1_safetransfer',	'ParkingZone will give you complete information about the carrier and their services. We select all of the carriers very carefully.'),
(113,	'services_page_transfer_sec2_grid1_heading',	'Convenience'),
(114,	'services_page_transfer_sec2_grid1_descp',	'You don’t have to worry about hiring a taxi when you will arrive at the terminal. Your taxi will and driver will be waiting for you at the terminal.'),
(115,	'services_page_transfer_sec2_grid2_heading',	'Price'),
(116,	'services_page_transfer_sec2_grid2_descp',	'Local taxi services can be a bit overpriced. The booking of a taxi through our website will provide you with quality services as well as reasonable prices.'),
(117,	'services_page_transfer_sec2_grid3_heading',	'Safety'),
(118,	'services_page_transfer_sec2_grid3_descp',	'ParkingZone works with only those service providers who are fulfilling our strict security policies and driver\'s data will also be shared with you.'),
(119,	'services_page_transfer_sec2_grid4_heading',	'Choice'),
(120,	'services_page_transfer_sec2_grid4_descp',	'ParkingZone provides you with a variety of services as well as choices of vehicles. You can choose the vehicle you want to travel at cheaper rates.'),
(121,	'site_twitter_title',	'The UK most popular choice for Airport Parking, ParkingZone give you the best deals at Gatwick, Heathrow, Stansted, Manchester and all major UK airports.'),
(122,	'site_og_title',	'The UK most popular choice for Airport Parking, ParkingZone give you the best deals at Gatwick, Heathrow, Stansted, Manchester and all major UK airports.'),
(123,	'site_author',	'Author'),
